body_html:
I use the script to manually freeze model , since there is dropout and Batch normalization in Mobilenet , I set is_training = False as the suggestions ( it seems like doing the same thing as slim tutorial ) . And MovingAverage doesn't apply in model.
But the accuracy is still terrible.
